Now, in this lesson, Jesus heals and teaches, and in each instance invites us.

00:00:25.728 --> 00:00:30.912
To distrust ourselves and put our trust in him

00:00:31.776 --> 00:00:33.696
Before we read, let's pray.

00:00:34.112 --> 00:00:40.672
Our Father in heaven, we ask that you would speak to our hearts and help us to hear Jesus. In his name I pray.

00:00:40.832 --> 00:00:42.048
Amen.

00:00:42.432 --> 00:00:45.920
Amen. Mark chapter 9, beginning at verse 14.

00:00:46.304 --> 00:00:56.352
And when they came to the disciples, they saw a great crowd around them, and scribes arguing with them. And immediately all the crowd, when they saw him, were greatly amazed.

00:00:55.872 --> 00:00:58.432
Amazed and ran up to him and greeted him.

00:00:58.464 --> 00:01:00.032
And he asked them,

