And he answered them, O faithless generation, how long am I to be with you? How long am I to bear with you? Bring him to me.

00:01:31.744 --> 00:01:40.896
And they brought the boy to him, and when the spirit saw him immediately, it convulsed the boy, and he fell on the ground and rolled about foaming at the mouth.

00:01:40.768 --> 00:01:45.792
And Jesus asked his father, how long has this been happening to him?

00:01:45.824 --> 00:01:47.008
And he said,

00:01:46.784 --> 00:01:48.224
From childhood.

00:01:48.224 --> 00:01:53.248
And it is often cast him into fire and into water to destroy him.

00:01:53.408 --> 00:01:55.296
But if you can do anything,

00:01:55.072 --> 00:01:57.312
Have compassion on us.

00:01:57.184 --> 00:01:58.816
And help us.

00:01:58.880 --> 00:02:01.792
And Jesus said to him, "If you can,

00:02:02.048 --> 00:02:05.088
All things are possible for one who believes

