Immediately the father of the child cried out and said, I believe, help my unbelief.

00:02:10.752 --> 00:02:20.800
And when Jesus saw that a crowd came running together, he rebuked the unclean spirit, saying to it, you mute and deaf spirit, I command you come out of him and never.

00:02:20.320 --> 00:02:22.144
And never enter him again.

00:02:21.888 --> 00:02:30.432
And after crying out and convulsing him terribly, it came out, and the boy was like a corpse, so that most of them said he is dead.

00:02:30.240 --> 00:02:34.656
But Jesus took him by the hand and lifted him up, and he arose.

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:39.200
And when he had entered the house, his disciples asked him privately.

00:02:39.104 --> 00:02:41.632
Why could we not cast it out?

00:02:41.696 --> 00:02:43.200
And he said to them,

00:02:42.976 --> 00:02:47.264
This kind cannot be driven out by anything but prayer.

00:02:47.872 --> 00:02:57.920
They went on from there and passed through Galilee, and he did not want anyone to know, for he was teaching his disciples, saying to them, The Son of Man is going to be delivered into the.

