00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:12.160
when they came to Capernaum.

00:03:12.032 --> 00:03:17.120
And when he was in the house, he asked them, what were you discussing on the way?

00:03:17.568 --> 00:03:23.392
But they kept silent, for on the way they had argued with one another about who was the greatest.

00:03:23.488 --> 00:03:26.592
And he sat down and he called the twelve

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:27.904
And he said to them,

00:03:27.808 --> 00:03:29.824
If anyone would be first.

00:03:29.696 --> 00:03:33.376
He must be the last of all, and servant of all.

00:03:33.312 --> 00:03:43.360
And he took a child and put him in the midst of them, and taking him in his arms, he said to them, Whoever receives one such child in my name receives.

00:03:42.880 --> 00:03:43.936
Receives me.

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:48.736
And whoever receives me receives not me, but him who sent me.

